\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {11}{\ignorespaces Before/after spectral refinement for the top-8 most improved test molecules. Black: DFT reference; orange: raw SpectraLoRA prediction; blue: ES-refined output. The refinement suppresses spurious peaks, sharpens real peaks, and improves spectral alignment without changing peak positions by more than ${\sim }$5~cm$^{-1}$.}}{20}{figure.11}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:es-before-after}{{11}{20}{Before/after spectral refinement for the top-8 most improved test molecules. Black: DFT reference; orange: raw SpectraLoRA prediction; blue: ES-refined output. The refinement suppresses spurious peaks, sharpens real peaks, and improves spectral alignment without changing peak positions by more than ${\sim }$5~cm$^{-1}$}{figure.11}{}}
